(3, 'About Us', 'two_columns_right', NULL, NULL, 'about-us', NULL, '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Bhoomisewa is an online marketplace for all your home decor and renovation needs. We are dedicated to bringing you shopper''s friendly creative portal exclusively for making your living space more homely.</p>\r\n<p>Now there is no need roaming and searching markets to look through home furnishings, home decor, lights, bath accessories, Modular Kitchen designs and much more that your home will need We Welcome you to bhoomisewa!! Create your living with best products, best quality , best prices and best designs with Us.</p>\r\n<h4>Our Team</h4>\r\n<p>We have a fully functional and professionally qualified team who is eager to serve you at each step and making your every shopping experience memorable with us.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Shubham Gupta : Founder of Bhoomisewa : </strong>Making impossible sounds like possible, our founder leaves no stone unturned to achieve company''s vision and customer satisfaction.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Nikita Maheshwari : Co Founder of Bhoomisewa : </strong>Impatient for perfection , our co - founder will never let go of any problem unresolved.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Rahul Arora : Co Founder of Bhoomisewa : </strong>Passionate by nature, he drives every work at hand passionately.</p>', '2015-09-13 05:45:27', '2015-10-21 13:46:39', 1, 0, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
