="item"><img alt="Checkout" src="http://cleo.weltpixel.com/images/demo-intro/checkout_screen.png" /></div>\r\n<div class="item"><img alt="Home Page" src="http://cleo.weltpixel.com/images/demo-intro/landing_screen.png" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<style><!--\r\n    .owl-item {\r\n        padding: 50px;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    #owl-brand {\r\n        background-color: #333;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    #owl-brand .item {\r\n        margin: 0 !important;\r\n        padding: 0 !important;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n    #owl-brand .owl-buttons {\r\n        display: block !important;\r\n    }\r\n--></style>\r\n<script type="text/javascript">// <![CDATA[\r\njQuery(document).ready(function($) {\r\n        var owl = $("#owl-brand");\r\n        owl.owlCarousel({\r\n            items : 5,\r\n            pagination : false,\r\n            rewindNav : true,\r\n            navigation : true,\r\n            itemsDesktopSmall : [979, 5],\r\n            itemsMobile : [479, 2],\r\n            navigationText : [''<i class="ion-ios7-arrow-left"></i>'', ''<i class="ion-ios7-arrow-right"></i>'']\r\n        });\r\n    });\r\n// ]]></script>\r\n<div class="section nobottommargin notopmargin notoppadding" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">\r\n<div class="w clearfix">\r\n<div class="row topmargin-lg bottommargin-sm">\r\n<div class="heading-title center">\r\n<h2>Features adapted to the 2015&rsquo;s ECOMMERCE market</h2>\r\n<p class="subtitle-txt">Developed by Certified Magento Developers, Cleo integrates stunning features that help you really customize your solution and offer an absolute smooth user experience for your clients.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6 bottommargin">\r\n<div class="feature-box fbox-right topmargin" data-animate="fadeIn">\r\n<div class="fbox-icon">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>Translation Ready</h3>\r\n<p>Multi-Store, Multi-Language and Multi-Concurrency ready</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="feature-box fbox-right topmargin" data-animate="fadeIn" data-delay="200">\r\n<div class="fbox-icon">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>Extensive Documentation</h3>\r\n<p>We have covered each &amp; everything in our Docs including Videos &amp; Screenshots.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="feature-box fbox-right topmargin" data-animate="fadeIn" data-delay="400">\r\n<div class="fbox-icon">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>LookBooks</h3>\r\n<p>Display your Content attractively using Parallax Sections with HTML5 Videos.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-4 col-md-4 hidden-sm bottommargin center"><img class="image-fade" alt="iphone 2" src="http://cleo.weltpixel.com/images/demo-intro/gif_pages.gif" /></div>\r\n<div class="col-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6 bottommargin">\r\n<div class="feature-box topmargin" data-animate="fadeIn">\r\n<div class="fbox-icon">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>Custom page width</h3>\r\n<p>Canvas provides support for Native HTML5 Videos that can be added to a Background.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="feature-box topmargin" data-animate="fadeIn" data-delay="200">\r\n<div class="fbox-icon">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>Sell Anything</h3>\r\n<p>Simple, Configurable, Bundle and Grouped Products Ready!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="feature-box topmargin" data-animate="fadeIn" data-delay="400">\r\n<div class="fbox-icon">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h3>Unlimited Sliders</h3>\r\n<p>Highlight your key content or special offers! Revolution Slider Included</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row clearfix w">\r\n<div class="heading-title center">\r\n<h2>Customers love user friendly websites!</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6"><img class="margin image-fade" alt="" src="http://cleo.weltpixel.com/images/demo-intro/3_iphones.png" /></div>\r\n<div class="col-md-6">\r\n<p class="subtitle-txt">To increase your revenues and avoid store bounce rate, your customers need to have an obvious, simple path from your website entrance to the product they are looking for. We spent many hours optimizing the layered navigation for mobile devices as well. The price slider along with the swatch options will offer your customers a second to none user experience.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- end w --></div>\r\n<div class="toggle">\r\n<div class="togglet wp-button wp-button-full wp-button-dark center bottommargin-lg">\r\n<div class="container clearfix">More than 27+ design feature. View them all!</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id="weltpixel_features" class="togglec" style="display: none;">{{block type="cms/block" block_id="weltpixel_features"}}</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="row clearfix w">\r\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12"><img class="image-fade" alt="Fashion Box" src="http://cleo.weltpixel.com/images/demo-intro/unlimited_colors.png" />\r\n<div class="heading-title center">\r\n<h3>Unlimited Colors</h3>\r\n<span class="center">Change the appearance of almost every element with a click on the color picker &ndash; no CSS knowledge required! You can simply change the color of all parameters: body, header, footer simply from the admin.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12"><img class="image-fade" alt="Fashion Box" src="http://cleo.weltpixel.com/images/demo-intro/newsletter_popup.png" />\r\n<div class="heading-title center">\r\n<h3>Newsletter Popup</h3>\r\n<span class="center">You can easily set after how many page views as well as time spent on the website you want to display the pop-up box. You can fully control the appearance of your popups by defining the following options: Display pages, Enable/Disable for mobile customers, pages before display, seconds before display, and many more...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12"><img class="image-fade" style="box-shadow: 0 0 20px -5px #ccc;" alt="Fashion Box" src="http://cleo.weltpixel.com/images/demo-intro/search_results.png" />\r\n<div class="heading-title center">\r\n<h3>Search Result Autosuggest</h3>\r\n<span class="center">Provide the most relevant search results after the third character is entered with this great feature! With the search preview showing store items matching search terms, customers can easily navigate to the desired product page. The fast and convenient Search Autocomplete and Suggest will enable your customers to view the list of suggestions based on any attribute such as product name, description, SKU, meta data, etc.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12"><img class="image-fade" style="box-shadow: 0 0 20px -5px #ccc;" alt="Fashion Box" src="http://cleo.weltpixel.com/images/demo-intro/one_page_checkout.png" />\r\n<div class="heading-title center">\r\n<h3>One Page Checkout</h3>\r\n<span class="center">Reduce checkout process from 6 to 1 step. By making checkout easier for customers, you will increase your revenue and conversion rate. Allows customers to use saved contact information. Autocomplete is enabled to allow customers to swiftly complete information fields with stored information from their browser.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12"><img class="image-fade" alt="Fashion Box" src="http://cleo.weltpixel.com/images/demo-intro/multiple_headers.png" />\r\n<div class="heading-title center">\r\n<h3>Multiple Header Styles</h3>\r\n<span class="center">Cleo has three types of header layouts to match any designs. The sticky header and the transparency option will make your website look clean and elegant.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="col-md-4 col-sm-12 col-xs-12"><img class="image-fade" style="box-shadow: 0 0 20px -5px #ccc;" alt="Fashion Box" src="http://cleo.weltpixel.com/images/demo-intro/instagram.png" />\r\n<div class="heading-title center">\r\n<h3>Instagram Feed</h3>\r\n<span class="center">Source social content in real-time for your customers.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- end wrapper -->\r\n<div class="section parallax nobottommargin" style="background-image: url(''http://www.weltpixel.com/cleo/cleo/assets/bg.jpg''); padding: 100px 0;" data-stellar-background-ratio="0.4">\r\n<div class="heading-block center">\r\n<h3>Who is